author: Cory Stieg
title: 72-year-old Arnold Schwarzenegger is working out at home — here are some of his moves you can do too
description: Arnold Schwarzenegger shared his home workout routine, complete with throwback photos to demonstrate the exercises. Take a look at some of the moves you can do too.
content: Arnold Schwarzenegger took to Reddit on Saturday to urge Americans to stay indoors during the COVID-19 pandemic and "focus on the things we do control," like our physical fitness. And you don't need fancy workout equipment or a streaming service to get a good… [+5986 chars]
